{
  "1874880": {
    "name": "武装突袭 重铸者",
    "steam_appid": 1874880,
    "required_age": "16",
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Arma Reforger》是一款纯正的冷战军事沙盒游戏，让你体验极度逼真的武器和游戏系统、规模宏大的地形以及丰富多样的定制选项。畅玩多人游戏、合作及单人游戏等诸多游戏模式，与其他玩家或者 AI 一起战斗，并通过游戏内创意中心的海量模组量身定制游戏的各个方面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>《Arma Reforger》是极为知名的《Arma》系列的最新之作，提供功能完善、创意十足且完全支持模组的平台，它必将重新定义军事模拟类游戏。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/f10ab29c3ca867b196b36ca0093a7dd9.avif?t=1770816362\" width=780 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以在 <i>Conflict</i> 游戏模式中体验激动人心的多人战斗，每场赛局可能持续一小时到到数天时间；你也可以在 <i>Game Master</i> 游戏模式中创建自己专属的任务并实时策划它们。在 <i>Combat Ops</i> 模式中与好友组队一起执行特别作战行动，或者在 <i>Capture &amp; Hold</i> 模式中畅享快节奏的战术玩法，感受肾上腺素飙升的感觉。对于独狼玩家，新的单人游戏战役<i>《Operation Omega》</i>有 5 个具有重复游玩价值的任务，而且额外场景<i>“Elimination”</i>和<i>“Air Support”</i>可提供数小时紧张刺激且充满沉浸感的游戏时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/83d5795edcb9083bdd7894adcac333d0.poster.avif?t=1770816362\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/83d5795edcb9083bdd7894adcac333d0.webm?t=1770816362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/7993da851634984ebdf144a5b1a3fd31.avif?t=1770816362\" width=780 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从 M16 独特的噼啪声到 BTR-70 的轰鸣声，我们在《Arma Reforger》的设计中力求真实还原每个战场元素。置身于子弹横飞的逼真交火，仅使用地图和指南针进行导航，并掌握一系列精心还原的冷战时代武器和载具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/2a9fe99696261f09708eb928caaa586e.poster.avif?t=1770816362\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/2a9fe99696261f09708eb928caaa586e.webm?t=1770816362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/907d5c245fc2c18ea88b94c500048c93.avif?t=1770816362\" width=780 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部署到三个规模宏大且细节丰富的岛屿，参加紧张刺激且充满沉浸感的开放世界军事行动。这些岛屿的风景令人惊叹，其郁郁葱葱的森林、田园诗般的城镇以及险峻的山脉为《Arma Reforger》的各种 PVP 模式、合作模式以及单人游戏模式提供了完美的舞台。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/c31857d9f0a78945f32168b5146cae07.poster.avif?t=1770816362\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/c31857d9f0a78945f32168b5146cae07.webm?t=1770816362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/6f8a2a027428226fda32d63833dcfe67.avif?t=1770816362\" width=780 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战争规模随着科古耶夫的加入而进一步扩大，这座标志性的岛屿最初亮相于《Arma：Cold War Assault》。在设定于 1989 年的全新单人战役中，穿梭于旧矿场的荒凉废墟，潜入秘密军事设施并身临其境地体验科古耶夫独特的氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/a649b79c8a4529ab11b35794ad21048a.poster.avif?t=1770816362\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/a649b79c8a4529ab11b35794ad21048a.webm?t=1770816362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/343bf195422b099e9a025574cf104b17.avif?t=1770816362\" width=780 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏内的创意中心，即时下载和安装由社区制作的海量模组。《Arma Reforger》的模组覆盖了各种时期和类型，为玩家提供丰富多样的武器、载具、资产、地形、游戏机制，甚至还有全新的游戏模式，让玩家能够根据自己喜爱的风格定制游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/90b4db10c4cbc72161e437f0e74e4332.poster.avif?t=1770816362\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874880/extras/90b4db10c4cbc72161e437f0e74e4332.webm?t=1770816362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 捷克语, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 乌克兰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
